      "message": "Just to make sure I understand - wuffs returned kErrorInInput for incrementalDecode (not startIncrementalDecode) on the first iteration of this loop, but we just never check for that? Maybe this test should just check the Result on each call to startIncrementalDecode and incrementalDecode, and return when it\u0027s not kSuccess, rather than expecting a specific behavior.",
